snippet.title: Official Loonyland Steam Release Trailer
snippet.description:
I had to make it, so you have to watch it! It's Loonyland! Still fun after all these years!

Add it to your wishlist IMMEDIATELY OR FACE THE CONSEQUENCES: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2876900/Loonyland_Halloween_Hill/

Big thanks to Androgeos, Circadian, and P-Tux7 for supplying me with footage I was too lazy to collect myself.
